                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>nōba yšīl īd-u min hēn nōba yšīl īd-u min hēn, ǧaʕ yiktilūn-u, rḥamt abū-y. w ǧāye umm-i turkuḏ̣ šāyle al-ʕaǧiyye gāyle: daḥḥǧu ʕalay-ye!</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
