                <ANNOTATION_VALUE>alḥaz aḏ̣rub al-ʕaǧiyye hāḏi ašīl-he azitt-he b-al-gāʕ aḍbaḥ-ha. az-zlime hāḏa taww-u ǧīʸ. mā-l-u ḥitt mā yrūḥ hū mā-l-u ʕalāga b-Sūriyye mā-l-u ʕalāga ᵊb-ḥade.</ANNOTATION_VALUE>
